- `sf-apex-pattern-scanner` (nuovo) вЂ” framework trigger, naming conventions, logging pattern
- `sf-integration-scanner` (giГ  esistente) вЂ” named credentials, remote sites, callout patterns
- `sf-test-analyzer` (giГ  esistente) вЂ” convenzioni test, coverage minima

